Scarlet Heart
Episode 34

24
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,460
Second Miss, be careful.

25
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,780
Aiya, Second Miss!

26
00:02:20,780 --> 00:02:23,260
That's against tradition! You're supposed to wait for Fourteenth Prince to lift the veil!

27
00:02:23,260 --> 00:02:24,260
Your servant, Chen'xiang.

28
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:25,280
Your servant, Luo'xia.

29
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,580
We pay our respects to Cefujin.

30
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:28,460
You may rise.

31
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:32,260
Wang'ye ordered us to serve Cefujin.

32
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:34,600
This must be Senior Sister Qiaohui.

33
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,940
In the future, if there's anywhere we are not attentive to in serving Mistress,

34
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:38,900
we will need much of your guidance.

35
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,960
Second Miss, look.

36
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,360
Where did Fourteenth Prince find such capable girls?

37
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,820
Their smiles are so sweet, honey almost flows out from them.

38
00:02:44,820 --> 00:02:46,500
Much thanks for your praise.

39
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:51,580
Wang'ye saw that I was pleasant and thus ordered me to serve Fujin to make her smile more.

40
00:02:51,580 --> 00:02:52,900
You may leave first.

41
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:54,060
- Yes.
- Yes.

42
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:59,200
Qiaohui, don't you find it strange?

43
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:01,420
Inside this estate, the atmosphere seems to be celebratory,

44
00:03:01,420 --> 00:03:03,460
but it doesn't feel like a wedding ceremony.

45
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:05,420
I was just pondering on the same thing.

46
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:07,900
From the time I entered until now, I've never seen a celebratory word.

47
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,160
I haven't seen the Fourteenth Prince.

48
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:12,200
Even up to this moment, I still don't see him.

49
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:14,560
It's my fault that I just praised him.

50
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,120
Qiaohui...

51
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,560
What did you just praise me for?

52
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,720
Greetings to the Fourteenth Prince!

53
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,560
It's alright, rise.

54
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,860
Are you tired?

55
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,460
Why don't you sit down for a bit.

56
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:34,080
Qiaohui, you still haven't answered me.

57
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,540
What did you just praise me for?

58
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:42,940
When your servant passed through the front gates,

59
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:44,880
I saw the entrance was quite festive.

60
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:47,020
I even praised Fourteenth Prince by saying

61
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:49,880
it was all thanks to your deep childhood friendship with Second Miss.

62
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:54,140
But right now, there's not even a 'xi' character anywhere.
(xi - happiness, two side by side characters for double happiness)

63
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:57,000
This is the problem with having a maid who grew up with you,

64
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,540
but who is older than you in age.

65
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,220
Isn't this what you taught her?

66
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:05,200
I heard Tenth Brother say that before you came to the Eighth Prince's estate,

67
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,000
Qiaohui was very obedient.

68
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:10,960
But after following this sly mouth of yours, that even Tenth Brother had to face soft barbs.

69
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,960
I...

70
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,660
The Emperor has decreed,

71
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,100
that we are not allowed to perform a big wedding ceremony.

72
00:04:17,340 --> 00:04:19,480
And the decorations inside the estate

73
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,100
are not allowed to include the word 'xi'.

74
00:04:22,179 --> 00:04:23,659
It was the Emperor.

75
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,159
Then how come the estate

76
00:04:26,159 --> 00:04:27,900
has lanterns and festive hangings?

77
00:04:28,980 --> 00:04:30,740
I didn't want you to see and think it's bare and gloomy,

78
00:04:30,740 --> 00:04:32,580
so I had it decorated simply.

79
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:35,440
I don't mind it.

80
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:38,060
But must you rebel against his words?

81
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:39,900
It's fine if it's not allowed.

82
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:42,000
Why must you two quarrel about these things?

83
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:45,000
If the Emperor hears about this, it will become yet another issue.

84
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,160
What is there to be afraid of?

85
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:49,180
I have the decree of the past Emperor.

86
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:51,140
Ruoxi,

87
00:04:51,140 --> 00:04:52,780
do you want to go out and meet the other people?

88
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:54,320
There's no need.

89
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:58,740
You also know, I have come here for peace and tranquility.

90
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:05,140
All right. Everything will be according to your wishes.

91
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,380
What is it?

92
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,700
This is a secret report.

93
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:31,620
Maertai Ruoxi wore a red veil to enter Fourteenth Prince's Estate?

94
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,500
Wasn't it ordered

95
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:36,700
not to allow this to be a formal traditional ceremony?

96
00:05:37,180 --> 00:05:38,860
Only she has the guts.

97
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:41,660
What's more,

98
00:05:42,339 --> 00:05:44,224
when she was eating with 14th Brother's other primary wives,

99
00:05:45,492 --> 00:05:47,633
she dared to leave the table before them

100
00:05:47,633 --> 00:05:49,620
and doesn't give them any face.

101
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,864
Her personality is very headstrong,

102
00:05:57,864 --> 00:05:59,702
so she doesn't respect some things.

103
00:06:02,366 --> 00:06:06,340
Looks like she doesn't care for 14th romantically at all.

104
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,660
Second Miss, don't write anymore.

105
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:19,780
You're not trying to be top scholar.

106
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:21,924
Let's go see Chen'xiang kick the shuttlecock.

107
00:06:25,718 --> 00:06:28,008
You wrote enough to fill half the chest.

108
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,280
Is it?

109
00:06:30,258 --> 00:06:31,767
I didn't even realize that

110
00:06:31,767 --> 00:06:32,953
I wrote that much.

111
00:06:38,735 --> 00:06:41,160
Second Miss wrote down sentimental feelings

112
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,256
that are revealed by each stroke.

113
00:06:43,969 --> 00:06:47,314
- Senior Qiao'hui, come quickly. Let's go play together.

114
00:06:47,314 --> 00:06:49,580
Second Miss, Chen'xiang is calling us.

115
00:06:50,613 --> 00:06:51,945
Well, all right then.

116
00:06:51,945 --> 00:06:53,967
You go first, I'll follow later.

117
00:06:53,967 --> 00:06:55,586
Then I'll stay outside to wait for you.

118
00:07:05,885 --> 00:07:07,300
Such a beautiful masterpiece,

119
00:07:09,077 --> 00:07:10,740
but mine only resembles his in appearance...

120
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,084
In my heart,

121
00:07:42,084 --> 00:07:43,744
there's only him and I left.

122
00:07:44,706 --> 00:07:47,157
Every small bit that he and I shared,

123
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:51,321
a smile, a joke,

124
00:07:51,321 --> 00:07:53,016
a sigh.

125
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:57,735
I selfishly put aside everyone else and then forget them.

126
00:07:57,735 --> 00:08:00,655
All that's left behind is everything he and I shared.

127
00:08:02,018 --> 00:08:06,685
For the first time, no one can bother us.

128
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,968
The first time

129
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,300
where I don't have any worries

130
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,510
and I can begin to love him again.

131
00:10:57,375 --> 00:10:58,822
It is my fault.

132
00:10:58,822 --> 00:11:00,680
It's not your fault.

133
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:03,760
Who's secretly spying?  Come out!

134
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:05,780
It's so cold,

135
00:11:05,780 --> 00:11:07,340
yet you're so hot-tempered.

136
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:13,980
Fu'jin,

137
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:16,460
between us, formality is not necessary.

138
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,480
I shall leave first then.

139
00:11:30,782 --> 00:11:32,753
Ruo'xi, if you want to see something,

140
00:11:32,753 --> 00:11:34,518
why not see it openly?

141
00:11:34,518 --> 00:11:35,940
Wouldn't that be much better?

142
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:51,322
The weather is so cold. You need to wear more clothes.

143
00:11:51,322 --> 00:11:53,480
You just perspired. Be careful about getting sick.

144
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:56,580
Between us two, who is colder?

145
00:11:59,287 --> 00:12:00,560
It's me who is colder.

146
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:01,720
It's cold.

147
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,620
Let's go inside the manor.

148
00:12:17,380 --> 00:12:19,465
Come take a look at what 14th Brother has written.

149
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:27,745
[ The rascal Liu'bang now controls Wei'yang Palace.]
(This was written by the real 14th Prince in history)

150
00:12:27,745 --> 00:12:31,421
[ The hero, Xiang'yu, has killed himself at He'xia.]

151
00:12:31,421 --> 00:12:34,240
[ It is well-known that brave heroes always end up pitiful.]

152
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:37,260
[ I can only sigh and bury my great ambition under the stones...]

153
00:12:41,423 --> 00:12:42,660
I think it is only 14th Brother

154
00:12:42,660 --> 00:12:45,940
speaking out of anger in a heated moment.

155
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:48,220
You should not take it too seriously.

156
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:51,560
He purposely wrote that letter to anger me,

157
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:55,231
but I could've chosen not to read his letter.

158
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:57,160
Emperor,

159
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:59,092
the secret letter from ZunHua has arrived.

160
00:13:25,202 --> 00:13:26,817
13th Brother.

161
00:13:28,460 --> 00:13:32,420
At that time when you persuaded me to let her go, you told me

162
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,740
she and 14th Brother are not in a real relationship.

163
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:42,580
Do you know what this secret letter writer person saw?

164
00:13:48,987 --> 00:13:52,520
"Ce Fu'jin of 14th Prince,

165
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:56,200
Maertaixi watched Wang Ye's sword dance and

166
00:13:57,205 --> 00:13:59,780
wiped the sweat from 14th Prince.

167
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:04,260
14th Prince warmed her hands.

168
00:14:05,244 --> 00:14:08,543
Both of them laughed together and

169
00:14:08,543 --> 00:14:10,540
held hands while walking."

170
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:15,660
In response, I believe,

171
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:16,920
firstly,

172
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:20,067
Ruo'xi has always thought a man-woman relationship as deeply as us.

173
00:14:20,067 --> 00:14:22,925
The more open-minded she is, the more she doesn't pay attention.

174
00:14:22,925 --> 00:14:23,875
Secondly, the person who wrote the letter

175
00:14:23,875 --> 00:14:26,920
wouldn't know what they were talking about, but

176
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:29,706
only heard them laughing.

177
00:14:29,706 --> 00:14:30,432
This kind of thing,

178
00:14:30,432 --> 00:14:32,980
from an outsider's viewpoint, would look very intimate,

179
00:14:32,980 --> 00:14:36,221
when in fact, the parties involved were not thinking that way at all.

180
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:41,180
Late at night, two people under the same roof,

181
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:43,698
what more is there to know other than what they're talking about?

182
00:14:43,698 --> 00:14:45,280
Please don't be upset.

183
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:48,920
Is it, you not only don't trust 14th Brother,

184
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:50,423
but you also

185
00:14:50,423 --> 00:14:52,300
don't even trust Ruo'xi?

186
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,760
Enough!

187
00:15:00,474 --> 00:15:02,320
From today onward,

188
00:15:02,980 --> 00:15:05,420
the things between 14th Brother and Ruo'xi,

189
00:15:07,225 --> 00:15:09,860
no need to report them to me anymore!

190
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:29,140
Open the door.

191
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:31,780
Let me in.

192
00:15:33,081 --> 00:15:36,700
Open the door, I want to drink with you.

193
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:39,460
Ruo'xi, open the door.

194
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:45,285
Ruo'xi...

195
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:49,620
Today I want to stay here to drink.

196
00:16:08,260 --> 00:16:12,780
Ruo'xi... come here.

197
00:16:20,929 --> 00:16:23,940
I know I shouldn't think this way,

198
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:27,980
but I don't feel it's at all fair!

199
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:33,360
If Imperial Father had given me the throne back then,

200
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:36,563
today, the person in control of the country

201
00:16:36,563 --> 00:16:38,620
would be me.

202
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:44,480
The endings for a few of my brothers would definitely have not turned out this way.

203
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:50,700
Long Keduo and Nian Gengyao, these dog servants,

204
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:54,560
would not be so arrogant!

205
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,468
14th Prince,

206
00:16:59,820 --> 00:17:01,800
the former Emperor's decision

207
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:05,320
was also not made overnight.

208
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,540
Right.

209
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:14,340
What can be done now?

210
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,459
What can I still do?

211
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:45,700
"Youthful chivalry without fear,
(Reciting a poem)

212
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:58,780
in bravery,

213
00:18:03,020 --> 00:18:09,980
...raise your hair up,

214
00:18:09,980 --> 00:18:15,620
stand up straight...

215
00:18:16,341 --> 00:18:22,140
...life and death,

216
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:28,140
... honor's importance..."

217
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:31,740
What did I do wrong?

218
00:18:34,560 --> 00:18:36,620
Why?

219
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:42,020
What did I do wrong in the end?

220
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:02,580
I'm sorry.

221
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:18,100
In those days, the three of us were like dogs that only fought.

222
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:22,420
Now, one has passed away. (Minghui, 8th Consort)

223
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:24,680
One is being imprisoned. (Mingyu, 10th Consort)

224
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:28,940
One sits quietly here,

225
00:19:28,940 --> 00:19:31,880
waiting for the flowers to wither. (Rouxi)

226
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:38,400
Ce'Fu'jin...

227
00:19:42,360 --> 00:19:43,520
Is she asleep?

228
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:46,340
Lately, Ce'Fu'jin has been dozing off quite often.

229
00:19:46,340 --> 00:19:48,660
I've heard people say

230
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:53,160
pregnant women sleep more often. Should we call a physician?

231
00:19:58,140 --> 00:20:02,260
Second Miss, Second Miss.

232
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,740
If you are tired,

233
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:06,540
lay on the bed to take a rest.

234
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,180
- Ce'Fu'jin!
-  Second Miss!
- Ce'Fu'jin!

235
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:20,340
- Ce'Fu'jin, what's wrong?
-  Second Miss?

236
00:20:20,340 --> 00:20:21,400
How are you, Ce'Fu'jin?

237
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,620
Go away!

238
00:20:23,460 --> 00:20:25,480
Leave!

239
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,400
You all go find one!

240
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,400
Go find one!  Go now!

241
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:29,660
14th Prince.

242
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:35,260
Ruoxi, don't worry.

243
00:20:35,260 --> 00:20:38,020
I will definitely find you a very good doctor.

244
00:20:38,020 --> 00:20:42,020
A few doctors already have said it's the end of the road.

245
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:44,900
Finding another one, he will only say the same.

246
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:47,440
That's because their knowledge is limited.

247
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:49,940
How can this be the end?

248
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:51,720
Back then the Imperial Physician

249
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:55,300
told me that too.

250
00:21:08,840 --> 00:21:10,540
Qiao'hui.

251
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:18,180
Second Miss.

252
00:21:21,802 --> 00:21:23,620
I'm sorry.

253
00:21:26,252 --> 00:21:28,050
I'm tired now.

254
00:21:42,581 --> 00:21:45,024
Second Miss.

255
00:22:00,140 --> 00:22:01,700
4th Prince.

256
00:22:08,736 --> 00:22:10,140
4th Prince.

257
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:12,447
4th Prince.

258
00:22:20,538 --> 00:22:25,740
4th Prince... 4th Prince...

259
00:22:26,054 --> 00:22:29,220
Second Miss, Second Miss.

