366
00:32:34,415 --> 00:32:36,050
I hope that

367
00:32:36,050 --> 00:32:38,934
after 13th Prince passes away,

368
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:42,742
you can personally tell Cheng'huan

369
00:32:44,066 --> 00:32:47,223
it is her mother's death anniversary.

370
00:32:51,301 --> 00:32:53,191
That will let Lu Wu,

371
00:32:53,191 --> 00:32:55,683
